.slide{
  .title{Slidedown - a new way for making slide decks!}
  .body{
    .h1{Welcome to Slidedown!}
    \\
    Have you ever wanted to make slides... .tt{.bf{in text}}?\\
    Well want no more! Slidedown - the premier text-first\\
    presentation framework with bahvioral markup is here!\\
    \\
    \\
    .o{• Text-first authoring with plain .tt{.sd} files}
    .o{• Behavioral markup drives effects (no JS editing needed)}
    .o{• Standalone HTML output with embedded assets}
    .typewriter{\> Cool effects like typewriter text!}
  }
}

.slide{
  .title{Markup at a Glance}
  .body{
    .h1{The Basics}

    Directives wrap content in curly braces with nesting support

    .code{.syntax{language=slidedown}
.slide{
  .title{Hello}
  .body{
    .o{Bullets reveal in order}
    .typewriter{Typed text}
    .code{.syntax{language=python}print("hi")}
  }
}}
    .o{• Directives wrap content: .tt{\.directive\{...\}}}
    .o{• Modifiers add styling: .tt{\.style\{align=center; width=60%\}}}
    .o{• Children become placeholders → compiled with their parent}
  }
}

.slide{
  .title{Effects - Typewriter}
  .body{
    .h1{Bring Your Slides to Life}

    Interactive behaviors without touching JavaScript

    .o{• .typewriter{Typewriter effect reveals characters}}
    .o{• Progressive snippet reveals}
    .o{• Inline formatting with .bf{bold} and .em{italic}}
    .o{• Combine effects for dynamic presentations}
  }
}

.slide{
  .title{Effects - ASCII Art}
